            // Example: (0,0) to (1,0) in 2 moves. (1,0) sum is 1 (odd). 2 moves (even). Impossible.
            // (0,0) -> (1,0) -> (0,0) is 2 moves, sum 0.
            // (0,0) -> (1,0) -> (2,0) is 2 moves, sum 2.
